import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { AuthService } from './services/auth.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { title = 'reddit'; isAuth: boolean; constructor(private authService: AuthService) { } ngOnInit() { this.authService.isAuthenticated$.subscribe(isAuth => { this.isAuth = isAuth; }); } }
